# Docs and conventions

- **API documentation** lives in **docs/api/**.
- **Authoritative guide:** [docs/api/docs.md](docs/api/docs.md) — project structure, path aliases (`@/` for `src/`, `$/` for `db/`), config and env, running the API, and conventions.
- When adding or changing API code (routes, DB, libs), follow the structure and conventions described there. Refer to the domain docs in docs/api/ (users.md, db.md, lib.md) as needed.
